@startuml seq_02_local_sign_in
title Sequence Diagram: UC-02.1 Sign In (Local)

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Auth Controller" as Controller
participant "Auth Service" as Service
participant "User Repository" as Repo
participant "Redis Cache" as Redis

User -> Frontend: (1.1) Open the Login page
User -> Frontend: (2.1) Enter username/email and password
User -> Frontend: (3.1) Submit credentials
Frontend -> Controller: (3.2) POST /api/auth/login {identifier, password}
Controller -> Service: (4.1) Validate login input
Service -> Repo: (5.1) Look up account by email or username
Repo --> Service: (5.2) User found (hashed_password)
Service -> Service: (6.1) Verify password and account status
Service -> Service: (7.1) Generate access and refresh tokens
Service -> Redis: (7.2) Store auth state (refresh token)
Service --> Controller: (8.1) Tokens and user info
Controller --> Frontend: (8.2) 200 OK
Frontend --> User: (8.3) Redirect to home page
@enduml
